      "body" : "It should be noted that with the autoconf system bitcoin uses, it can be modified to install `bitcoind` in `${PREFIX}/sbin` and those who want it in `${PREFIX}/bin` can use a configure switch to make that the directory. However as the autoconf is currently set up, there is no configure switch to `bitcoind` in `${PREFIX}/sbin` that would not also put `bitcoin-cli`, `bitcoin-tx`, and `bench_bitcoin` in `${PREFIX}/sbin`\r\n\r\nSo changing the autoconf files would allow `bitcoind` to be installed in `${PREFIX}/sbin` in accordance with the FHS and LSB while leaving the others in `${PREFIX}/bin` where they belong - but for those who really want it all in `${PREFIX}/bin` can do so with `--sbindir=/usr{,/local}/bin` as a configure switch.",
      "created_at" : "2016-03-02T11:35:00Z",
